A region is a seperate location in world
There are many region in the AWS
Each regions contain many availability zones
An Availability zone has one or more data centres
resources can be used on multiple availability zones to have a low down time
all these regions are connected by aws network 

Aws outposts
----------------
AWS outposts brings AWS infrastructure and services to virtually on premises allowing to run the AWS services on premises

AWS local zones
----------------
AWS  local zone is an extension of an AWS region 
it is available in metropolitan area close to user premises 
It is used when there is requirement of low latency

